# NVIDIA GPU Support — Headless/Compute Only (no X11/GLX)
# Debian bookworm has no nvidia-headless metapackage (Ubuntu-only).
# These packages provide compute support without pulling X11/Xorg/GLX deps.
# nvidia-cuda-toolkit is NOT needed — Ollama bundles its own CUDA runtime.
dkms
linux-headers-amd64
nvidia-kernel-dkms
nvidia-driver-bin
nvidia-smi
nvidia-persistenced
firmware-nvidia-gsp
libcuda1
libnvidia-ml1
nvidia-modprobe
